---

<section style="background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 60px 0;">
  <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px;">
    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; gap: 60px; align-items: flex-start;">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Heading + Button + Image -->
      <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
        <h1 style="color: #111827; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 20px 0; line-height: 1.2; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
          Our Company
        </h1>
        
        <a href="#" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: #3b82f6; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 32px;">
          Join our team
          <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 10 10" style="display: inline-block;">
            <g fill-rule="evenodd">
              <path d="M0 5h7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></path>
              <path d="M1 1l4 4-4 4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"></path>
            </g>
          </svg>
        </a>
        
        <img 
          src="/hero-bg.jpg" 
          alt="LinxCosmo"
          style="width: 100%; height: auto; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 4px;"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Description -->
      <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 0;">
        <div style="color: #374151; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7;">
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            LinxCosmo &ndash; a dynamic and innovative company dedicated to enhancing everyday life through our unique and creative lifestyle products. At the core of our brand is a vision to connect and unify the myriad elements of modern living, bringing together functionality, style, and sustainability.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            Linx Cosmo was founded with the belief that thoughtfully designed products can transform ordinary spaces into extraordinary experiences. We specialize in crafting a diverse range of items for the home, garden, outdoor adventures, pet care, personal protection, sports, and beauty &ndash; all with a commitment to quality and a nod to the natural world.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            Our team of talented designers and engineers are passionate about pushing the boundaries of conventional design. We draw inspiration from the latest trends, as well as time-honored traditions, to create products that not only meet the needs of our customers but also spark joy and wonder.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
            As a company, Linx Cosmo is more than just a purveyor of fine goods; we are a community of dreamers, doers, and difference-makers. We believe in the power of creativity to make a positive impact on the world and are committed to using our platform to foster a more connected and vibrant global society.
          </p>
          <p style="margin: 0;">
            Join us on this journey as we continue to explore, innovate, and inspire. Welcome to Linx Cosmo &ndash; where every product tells a story and every purchase makes a difference.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
